498
00:37:35,669 --> 00:37:38,297
Reap! Reap!

499
00:37:38,472 --> 00:37:41,441
I seem to feel a monsoon dripping in.

500
00:37:42,609 --> 00:37:45,077
It was nice to see you again, Dad.

501
00:37:47,581 --> 00:37:50,607
- Bye, Mom.
- Goodbye, dear.

502
00:37:51,084 --> 00:37:54,178
You tell Dick that he's a lucky man.

503
00:37:54,955 --> 00:37:58,254
Not everybody gets
a real chance to be tested.

504
00:37:58,759 --> 00:38:01,023
You tell him that I'm jealous.

505
00:38:01,628 --> 00:38:06,964
- I'm sure he'll be really thrilled, Dad.
- Don't forget to tell him I'm jealous too.

506
00:38:10,637 --> 00:38:12,195
So long.

507
00:38:15,308 --> 00:38:17,037
Bye-bye.

508
00:38:42,102 --> 00:38:45,697
