707
00:50:59,539 --> 00:51:02,007
- Hello, Mr. Harper.
- Hello, Carol.

708
00:51:02,175 --> 00:51:04,439
Jane, what is Carol doing here?

709
00:51:04,610 --> 00:51:06,601
I'm going with you
to your meeting tonight.

710
00:51:06,779 --> 00:51:10,078
You are not. You're staying here.
